Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Written by leading software professionals, InfoQ’s Flash Briefing delivers the latest headlines and summaries on tools and libraries from firms such as Google, Lyft, Netflix, and more.

Major topics include updates to languages including Java, Kotlin, C#, Swift, Go, and JavaScript, patterns and approaches for Microservices and other modern architectural styles, AI, ML and Data Engineering, DevOps, and software management techniques including Lean/Kanban, Holocracy and Sociocracy.
